{"tid":2344310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平打俾普京：你做大時  我做細 合作共贏 對抗分化","createTime":"2020-12-28T15:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T23:10:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a29ea4ca1f927e7af269707d3932647fbda3c7b7","tid":2344310,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T15:14:42.000Z","msg":"習近平與普京通電話 提出中俄在更深層次推進合作<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平， 晚上同俄羅斯總統普京通電話，習近平說，新型冠狀病毒疫情大流行對人類生命安全形成空前挑戰，危難時刻，中俄守望相助，共克時艱，在涉及彼此核心利益問題，繼續堅定相互支持，他提出，中俄要以明年慶祝睦鄰友好合作條約簽署20週年為契機，在更大範圍、更寬領域、更深層次上推進雙方合作，加強發展戰略對接，他說，中俄關係不受國際風雲變幻影響，不受任何其他因素干擾，中俄加強戰略協作，能夠有效抵禦打壓分化兩國的任何圖謀。<br />\n<br />\n普京表示，願同習近平繼續發揮戰略引領作用，確保俄中關係在新的一年得到新的發展，兩國繼續在涉及彼此核心利益的問題相互堅定支持，密切在國際事務的戰略協調與合作。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2372557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2372557&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=597ed2af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2372557</a>"},{"pid":"d0280a91fb086193b143dc8b5e36e019c3b1dc7f","tid":2344310,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DX_KpQfVMAEI183.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDX_KpQfVMAEI183.jpg&h=ca31fc0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/41718451_1765839053543734_4600158321909956608_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=X_Ef_HSM56sAX-82BnU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=51559e00520ee78b5bee244cb1ebb7a5&amp;oe=600F5A86\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F41718451_1765839053543734_4600158321909956608_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DX_Ef_HSM56sAX-82BnU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg6-1.